code: import*as axiosHelper from"./api_helper";export const subscribePushNotification=async payload=>{const data=await axiosHelper.post("/subscriptions/push-notification",payload);if(data.isError){throw new Error(data.message);}return data;};export const unsubscribePushNotification=async endpoint=>{const data=await axiosHelper.del("/subscriptions/push-notification",{data:{endpoint}});if(data.isError){throw new Error(data.message);}return data;};
